Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剝奪沃爾特少校的職權 即刻逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,655)\fs30}Walter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雷恩將軍命令中止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入坐標 進入攻擊態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我的戰友…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都去搜尋生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,質問者型…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(596,655)}Sphinx
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我攻擊了友軍…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了…有人活著嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我們贏不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 究竟是為了什麼 為了什麼而戰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曠日持久的戰爭讓世界凋敝不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能夠理解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭是否也就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的角落中等待破土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是日本在戰亂中毀滅之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為傳承和平這一文化而建造的人工島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾經的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地區大賽就快到了 鼓起幹勁來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香明白 要老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香美香 你可別出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續繼續…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她就想起過去的一騎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 回去的時候上一騎那兒吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你討厭我做的飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}堂馬廣登特別節目 追蹤神秘巨型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢廣登是做了多少節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹也是太有奉陪精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 無聊透頂 天氣還熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我想去Alvis上班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別光學打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得繼承島上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那起碼裝個空調啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好 里奈前輩…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事 鏑木？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你不是昨天就買過這本了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那個…這本是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說鏑木 你是學生會長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道買漫畫 七夕祭典的準備都做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個…里奈前輩不在討論就沒法進行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠不爭氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然下次到一騎前輩那裡一起討論？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 里奈前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之後有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我在上班啊 怎麼可能會有空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是機體的設計 更要學習實際組裝時的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ改 上臂引擎安裝完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進行FTP試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連接確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越來越熟練了呢 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(788,655)\fs30}Kanon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了媽媽的教導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡可是職員兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 羽佐間老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天待在這兒要悶出病來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是想去一騎那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒無所謂…去哪裡都成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不希望再有人駕駛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又要把它組裝起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到卡農會去學工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年紀技術卻很了得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是想做你徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乾脆退休算了 畢竟還得畫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真的是駕駛員培養教材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊 西尾老師開口的事沒法推託啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該吃飯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老規矩 去吃咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎 會趕不上午市的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有問題的 讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御門的 東西我搬到裡面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老爸教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個 一騎哥 有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午的研究收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子準備還沒好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過會兒再來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧 吃飯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是暉咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是 不過菜名加上廚師的名字是這裡的規矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如一騎咖喱什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是溝口先生擅自加的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很尊敬一騎前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見和溝口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾天一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧我還以為能和遠見前輩一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已捕捉到不明機體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}unknown follow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入自動瞄準程式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:22:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這招怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定目標 發射飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Fox-One
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你超前了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}run out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因為自己飛得快就把敵人給超了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又輸給溝口先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要是實戰 就是我被打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace 申請繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK Arrows 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(748,655)}lead again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}will-call
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你別這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 坐在大飛機上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽她啊 最近總是這樣淨跟幻想中的朋友說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為沒有同齡的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得不用太擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很感性 所以我就是放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐在飛機上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了呢 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,655)\fs30}Emery
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.84,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極其一般
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.23,0:24:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.95,0:24:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來教你什麼是料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比預定溫度還高了兩度
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.46,0:24:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要修正才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人啊 真是笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:24:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐套餐兩份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有兩杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.46,0:25:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是皆城燉菜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我們沒點這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 賣相還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.81,0:25:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一堆男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼連總士都上陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.10,0:25:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農是蜜瓜雪頂和…請用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.44,0:25:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼啊 我可沒點這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.07,0:25:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免費贈送
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你常常來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.89,0:25:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是不…討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有30次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.09,0:25:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,複診是在下星期 別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.26,0:25:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的成人禮也是那時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可得來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 總是承蒙你關照了 劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:25:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下次見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.97,0:26:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心完我的身體就開始擔心一騎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.96,0:26:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.18,0:26:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 總是操心別人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.79,0:26:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹也做做自己想做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.57,0:26:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.89,0:26:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如跟你一起吃吃飯什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.90,0:26:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.78,0:26:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見學航空 卡農學工科 劍司學醫療 要投身教育
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都決定了各自的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.46,0:26:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士你搞研究嗎 感覺挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.68,0:26:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？在咖啡館當廚師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 還挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.58,0:26:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想讓當年的王牌駕駛員的寶貴經驗發揮餘熱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.28,0:26:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當教官也是個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些痕跡 不開法芙娜了也還是留著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是尼伯龍根連接導致的小規模同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(433,655)\fs30}Nibelungen
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.68,0:26:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會找到治療方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始學些什麼 做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.71,0:27:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後這些事卻以未完成收場 我不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.49,0:27:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是這樣的嗎 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.44,0:27:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有希望恢復的 別太悲觀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.85,0:27:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.20,0:27:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.24,0:27:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼長的時間 足夠我做心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.19,0:27:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何況現在眼睛也能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是和平安穩的 重要的夥伴生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.14,0:27:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我會一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.62,0:27:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.04,0:27:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去下層區域嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在去生物圈的實驗室之前看看乙姬的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(457,655)}biosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.13,0:27:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上你讀的是博士課程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改成特種醫療了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.85,0:28:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見醫生對我說 這兩方面都是照顧乙姬所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.48,0:28:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.73,0:28:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.53,0:28:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和乙姬為我們所做的事相比
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.62,0:28:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的世界還在繼續戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.64,0:28:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據所羅門的應答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰火反倒是擴大了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.66,0:28:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬明明那麼渴望和平
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.17,0:28:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太令人悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.06,0:29:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.49,0:29:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你一直保護著這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.67,0:29:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼了 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.22,0:29:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對什麼東西起反應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.85,0:29:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 不明機體接近
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.85,0:29:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}註：CDC=作戰指揮中心(Combat Direction Center)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.53,0:29:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,90秒後將到達防護罩外沿
