Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標情報入庫 比對結果
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.13,0:29:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,655)\fs30}Target Merge
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.88,0:29:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-300 Super Galaxy 目標為人類軍大型運輸機
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.71,0:29:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍…？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感應到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.95,0:30:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一個十分美麗的島上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.71,0:30:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.28,0:30:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.86,0:30:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾梅莉好像也感應到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.68,0:30:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想讓我們見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.46,0:30:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫CDC 緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 維持距離跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,655)\fs30}Follow Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.55,0:31:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彙報情況
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到訓練中的紅隼戰鬥機報告
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,655)\fs30}Kestrel
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.80,0:31:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍運輸機正在靠近 緊急事態發生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於防護罩外確認到質量不明的迴轉體
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(901,655)}worm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門系統沒有應答
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,655)\fs30}Shlomo
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有機庫啟動迎擊態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.95,0:31:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,655)\fs30}burg
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1 第2重力波防護罩已展開
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,655)\fs30}Welle Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.92,0:31:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航路不變 法芙娜準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.45,0:31:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動手 敵人還沒有發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.18,0:31:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍只是在一味地逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放他們離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住區傳來通信請求 是日野家發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.44,0:31:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接過來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.40,0:31:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.24,0:31:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.84,0:31:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她說請救助那架飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}拜託了 媽媽 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別擔心 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.89,0:31:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要激動 正在幫你問了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.36,0:31:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}今天有工作的人員請立即進入應急態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.80,0:31:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}各位島民請勿外出 等待最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.85,0:31:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}隨著應急體制的啟動 第一……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.91,0:31:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}防禦幕牆已就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.91,0:31:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\pos(575,60)\fs30}waffeladen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.42,0:32:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}向島防衛線 剛瑠島控制區……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,200)\frz22\frx12\fry-12}出擊要求播報
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕果然棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.19,0:31:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說彗 同樣的雜誌你昨天就買過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.32,0:31:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.56,0:31:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改成出擊要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段視頻的燈光打得一般般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.59,0:32:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別錄太多版啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.43,0:32:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.93,0:32:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說要實戰 我們是不是也能駕駛法芙娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.09,0:32:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連接測試都沒做過就上？應該只是觀戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.99,0:32:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 我都還沒像廣登前輩那樣做好頭盔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西根本不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.17,0:32:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將到達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.01,0:32:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.25,0:32:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的前輩留給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.54,0:32:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣登前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.13,0:32:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.74,0:32:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.65,0:32:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.30,0:32:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把護身頭盔給她沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.26,0:32:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我們能開法芙娜的時間也沒剩幾年了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.07,0:32:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁現在讓她繼承了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.07,0:33:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.41,0:33:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能主動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.28,0:33:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.95,0:33:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門系統發出應答 敵人很可能在200秒內實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.25,0:33:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向50° 減速航行 防護罩部分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.19,0:33:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅隼戰鬥機引導運輸機降落到海面
